Podoprionidae 
<bibRefCitation author="Lowry" box="[551,857,958,984]" pageId="1" pageNumber="10" refString="Lowry, J. K. &amp; Stoddart, H. E. (1996) New Lysianassoid amphipod species from Namibia and Madagascar (Lysianassidae Dana, 1849 and Podoprionidae fam. nov.). Bolletino del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale, Verona, 20 (1993), 225 - 247." type="journal article" year="1996">
